                  <h2>ABOUT US</h2>
                  <p>CubaModela is the Online Network of Professionals of the fashion and photography industry in Cuba. Our mission is to connect cuban models and cuban photographers from Cuba with national and international clients. We provide a space for personalized advertising through the profiles that will constitute the fundamental criterion of selection to find jobs.</p>
